  "notes": [
    "plugins/blocklist.json is intentionally excluded from this pack: it is runtime state, not authored policy.",
    "rules/project/*.md files are operator scratch (in-flight initiative context) and are included here for full wipe-and-rehydrate fidelity. They are not durable doctrine and may rotate or expire.",
